    "body": "### Description\n\nThe feature to force stop a language server with `++force` (https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/pull/2294) appears to have been removed (I assume in the transition from `require('lspconfig')` to `vim.lsp`).\n\nTo reproduce:\n- Start a language server\n- `:LspStop ++force`",
